Author: HoldenCaulfield7
Text: Don’t sweat it. Don’t bring it up unless someone asks. They might not have even read it. If someone asks, be honest, say that you were reading about the importance of intermittent fasting (it’s cool and common now and wayyyyyy more cute than saying the scary word: ED).

Author: under_glasses
Text: I wouldn’t stress about it. If they didn’t say something immediately, I doubt they will at all. Can always brush it off and say they misread it or something if they mention it.
